{"tid":790530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰160億今日實施 無人講？","createTime":"2018-08-23T05:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T08:34:51.000Z","uid":81698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef73366f7b60cbca733d55a29627c3e7f5a5aa5b","tid":790530,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國對中國祭出的第二輪關稅制裁，在今（23日）中午正式生效，中國279項約160億美元（約新台幣4800億）進口商品將被加徵25%關稅，對此，中國宣布對美約160億美元商品加徵25%關稅也即刻正式實施。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，根據中國《國務院關稅稅則委員會關於對原產於美國500億美元進口商品加徵關稅的公告》，中國對美約160億美元商品加徵25%關稅於以於今中午12點正式實施，中國商務部指出，美國的關稅措施違反了世界貿易組織（WTO）的規定，中國將會向WTO提出申訴，要在WTO的機制下解決紛爭，並且會實施必要的回擊。<br />\n<br />\n此次中美加徵關稅，是繼今年7月6日美國對中國340億美元（約新台幣1兆）進口商品關稅制裁，中國也對美545項約340億美元商品加徵關稅後，中美之間貿易戰再次短兵相接。<br />\n<br />\n本次美國的新關稅，瞄準了中國279項商品徵收25%進口關稅，列入制裁清單的商品包含了半導體、化學品、塑料品、機車、電動車等，而中國對美方加徵關稅的333項商品中，汽車類則佔據超過一半。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2528487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2528487&d=WAyJM2esBSIt0x96w2cgd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f35fbb5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2528487&h=87e50f5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2528487</a>"},{"pid":"c2aa92ce41a261a504791b7a07dc19530ac79e51","tid":790530,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"快啲升級 一次過全部加稅啦 仲慢慢加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03902eb31c3d7adf2ebfcae16d228c76ea7e7fa","tid":790530,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/135613_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F135613_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=5c1f5974&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7443efd26419b25420f13122f02113d9ae6c901","tid":790530,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"160億美金濕濕碎"},{"pid":"dc6993f6387035c97be328bc188dceec30225b29","tid":790530,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"9月7日！！！！正"},{"pid":"2e9b5c7119309d1b58b39587517b09c7925880ac","tid":790530,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742c36e66ba39cd1a38e042dfbdbd5f3076ad204","tid":790530,"uid":181432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"有入講左啦！"},{"pid":"39dbb67ce6c948087c3b8a08d6cc8203453007c0","tid":790530,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"第一日炒?<br />\n入晒市啦。"}]}